    "body": "<!-- .github/pull_request_template.md -->\r\n\r\n## 📌 Description\r\n\r\nthe plan method in BatchPrefillWithPagedKVCacheWrapper will compute max query len by using qo_indptr_host. However, previous code only get the maximum value of qo_indptr, which is incorrect.\r\n\r\n\n\n<!-- This is an auto-generated comment: release notes by coderabbit.ai -->\n\n## Summary by CodeRabbit\n\n## Release Notes\n\n* **Bug Fixes**\n  * Improved computation of maximum sequence length to correctly calculate per-sequence token limits, ensuring more accurate resource allocation when processing batched sequences.\n\n<!-- end of auto-generated comment: release notes by coderabbit.ai -->",
